01:01:05.375 --> 01:01:06.958
That's my daytime job.

01:01:09.791 --> 01:01:11.791
- How is Eva?
- Fine.

01:01:12.833 --> 01:01:16.791
- She wants news about you.
- Does she talk about me?

01:01:18.208 --> 01:01:20.208
She thinks about you all the time.

01:01:21.500 --> 01:01:22.958
How do you know?

01:01:24.333 --> 01:01:27.750
Because all she has in her mind
is getting you out of here.

01:01:31.875 --> 01:01:35.500
She told me you are innocent.

01:01:37.083 --> 01:01:38.666
How did you end up here?

01:01:42.583 --> 01:01:44.000
Didn't Eva tell you?

01:01:52.750 --> 01:01:56.458
