to smuggle for him.

01:02:00.500 --> 01:02:02.625
You didn't tell that to the sheriff?

01:02:03.500 --> 01:02:05.208
- No.
- Why?

01:02:07.833 --> 01:02:10.333
I was afraid of what could happen
with her.

01:02:13.041 --> 01:02:14.666
And how did you meet?

01:02:14.750 --> 01:02:16.416
- I went after him.
- Why?

01:02:20.833 --> 01:02:22.166
To ask for money.

01:02:27.458 --> 01:02:29.791
I wanted to give my mom
a decent burial.

01:02:33.083 --> 01:02:34.541
She was very sick.

01:02:38.333 --> 01:02:41.291
