01:02:44.958 --> 01:02:46.291
Never.

01:03:15.125 --> 01:03:18.500
A worried man
Walking very worried

01:03:18.625 --> 01:03:21.750
No one in front of me
Nothing by my side

01:03:21.875 --> 01:03:23.958
A woman on my lap

01:03:24.375 --> 01:03:27.333
