- Thanks.

01:03:33.833 --> 01:03:37.000
Eyes to the sky
With an old boy's look

01:03:37.125 --> 01:03:39.083
I'm well dressed

01:03:39.625 --> 01:03:42.458
Waiting for the last train

01:03:44.750 --> 01:03:46.500
Standing
On a scaffold

01:03:46.583 --> 01:03:49.875
With my neck in a noose

01:03:52.458 --> 01:03:55.250
I have a second and a half
More or less

01:03:55.333 --> 01:03:57.708
