01:04:00.083 --> 01:04:03.458
Crazy people
Weird times

01:04:03.875 --> 01:04:06.666
I'm locked up
I cannot reach

01:04:06.791 --> 01:04:09.416
- All good?
- I cared

01:04:09.708 --> 01:04:12.625
