01:06:04.750 --> 01:06:07.166
- She did them herself.
- Wow.

01:06:07.250 --> 01:06:09.208
This is for you, Celeste.

01:06:09.291 --> 01:06:10.875
- Thank you.
- This is for you, Imã.

01:06:10.958 --> 01:06:12.333
Thank you so much, Odair.

01:06:15.875 --> 01:06:18.166
Oh my, this crochet is gorgeous!

01:06:20.333 --> 01:06:21.666
- That's it.
- Thank you.

01:06:24.125 --> 01:06:26.208
- See you later.
- Later.

