Don't you?
Don't you?

01:07:21.500 --> 01:07:26.041
You had me several years ago

01:07:26.125 --> 01:07:29.125
When I was still quite naive

01:07:29.833 --> 01:07:30.791
You look great.

01:07:30.875 --> 01:07:34.875
When you said
That we made such a pretty pair

01:07:35.041 --> 01:07:38.000
And that you would never leave

01:07:39.416 --> 01:07:43.791
But you gave away the things you loved

01:07:43.875 --> 01:07:47.333
And one of them was me

01:07:47.833 --> 01:07:51.625
I had some dreams
They were clouds in my coffee

01:07:52.000 --> 01:07:54.333
Clouds in my coffee, and

