01:08:08.791 --> 01:08:12.125
Don't you?
Don't you?

01:08:19.916 --> 01:08:21.082
Kinsman, do you--

01:08:21.957 --> 01:08:25.000
- Oh, sorry.
- No, that's fine, cousin.

01:08:25.082 --> 01:08:26.582
- That's fine.
- He's cute.

01:08:26.666 --> 01:08:29.041
Pedro, this is Celeste, my cousin.

01:08:29.125 --> 01:08:31.500
Pedro translated
"You're So Vain" for me.

01:08:31.582 --> 01:08:34.457
Oh, cool, it was really nice.

01:08:35.416 --> 01:08:36.500
Thanks.

01:08:36.582 --> 01:08:38.916
Imã, were you with Joca?

01:08:39.875 --> 01:08:41.666
I helped to choose.

01:08:41.750 --> 01:08:44.500
So, I sent him a message

01:08:44.582 --> 01:08:47.082
saying that I was super touched

01:08:47.375 --> 01:08:50.707
and that I loved it.
He replied with a happy emoji face.

01:08:50.791 --> 01:08:54.875
- You didn't like his happy emoji?
- No, it's not that. It's just--

01:08:55.375 --> 01:08:57.125
What does that mean?

01:08:57.207 --> 01:09:01.125
Like "Oh, I'm glad you liked the gift,
but we are done."

01:09:01.207 --> 01:09:03.957
The happy emoji means
he is happy, that's all.

01:09:06.000 --> 01:09:07.500
What do you think, Pedro?

01:09:09.000 --> 01:09:10.832
- What is the context?
- What?

01:09:11.375 --> 01:09:14.041
You broke up?
How was the relationship?

01:09:14.375 --> 01:09:15.875
Oh, it's...

01:09:16.207 --> 01:09:18.791
Well, he cheated on me.
I was really hurt

01:09:18.875 --> 01:09:21.082
and I made a scene so he would leave.

01:09:21.166 --> 01:09:24.000
- Some 3D scene.
- Then he sent the baby shoes?

01:09:24.541 --> 01:09:28.125
Yes, with this note: "Uncle Imã, love it."

01:09:28.207 --> 01:09:29.832
I think he is a nice guy.

01:09:30.000 --> 01:09:32.541
And that he loves you and will fight
to get you back.

01:09:33.000 --> 01:09:35.082
- You really think?
- I do.

01:09:36.625 --> 01:09:39.500
- Well, I gotta go.
- No, stay! I need to go.

01:09:39.582 --> 01:09:42.207
No, I have a class to teach
in the morning.

01:09:42.750 --> 01:09:45.625
Congrats, it was really special.

01:09:57.041 --> 01:09:58.250
- Bye.
- Bye.

01:10:15.250 --> 01:10:17.250
Why do you have that face?

01:10:19.250 --> 01:10:20.416
Nothing.

01:10:21.583 --> 01:10:23.500
I know you. Spill the beans.

01:10:32.291 --> 01:10:34.625
You and Odair?

01:10:38.750 --> 01:10:40.666
- Yes.
- I knew it!

01:10:43.875 --> 01:10:45.958
So, that story with Milene won't--

01:10:47.083 --> 01:10:48.000
Yes!

01:10:48.833 --> 01:10:52.250
Shi-- Eva, Eva, Eva, Eva.

01:10:53.208 --> 01:10:54.500
Don't worry.

01:10:57.125 --> 01:10:58.333
I do worry.

01:11:07.083 --> 01:11:08.208
You are nuts!

01:11:09.375 --> 01:11:10.416
You are nuts.

01:11:16.708 --> 01:11:18.333
I missed you.

01:11:35.750 --> 01:11:39.000
I wasn't pretending,
I did miss you.

01:11:42.583 --> 01:11:44.416
Your visit did me some good.

01:11:47.083 --> 01:11:48.666
I even dreamed again.

01:11:51.875 --> 01:11:52.791
That's good.

01:11:57.583 --> 01:11:58.625
Is this the guy?

01:12:07.250 --> 01:12:08.458
It is him.

01:12:14.833 --> 01:12:16.541
You'll be out of here soon.

01:12:17.666 --> 01:12:19.166
You want me out?

01:12:20.125 --> 01:12:21.833
You will be out of here.

01:12:25.208 --> 01:12:27.791
Tell Eva I miss her really badly?

01:12:31.750 --> 01:12:33.416
I miss her kisses.

01:12:37.583 --> 01:12:40.083
I dream of putting my mouth on hers.

01:12:43.625 --> 01:12:46.458
I miss her scent, her body,

01:12:47.208 --> 01:12:49.166
the way she touched me.

01:12:54.083 --> 01:12:55.208
Will you tell her?

01:13:03.541 --> 01:13:05.041
Excuse me.

01:13:05.125 --> 01:13:06.333
Ângelo!

01:13:06.583 --> 01:13:09.000
- Where were you?
- Where is Odair?

01:13:09.083 --> 01:13:11.666
He was here, but left.
It seems he had an issue at home.

01:13:11.750 --> 01:13:13.583
- Are you okay?
- I'm great.

01:13:13.666 --> 01:13:16.166
Call him, please.
I'm worried.

01:13:16.250 --> 01:13:18.333
I saw some dudes around the corner.

01:13:18.416 --> 01:13:20.958
I'm worried, I didn't like it.
Very weird.

01:13:22.166 --> 01:13:23.666
- Very weird.
- Voicemail.

01:13:24.125 --> 01:13:25.458
Try his house, please.

01:13:49.958 --> 01:13:50.791
I...

01:13:52.000 --> 01:13:53.125
Deaf.

01:13:53.875 --> 01:13:57.583
My son not here.

01:14:03.125 --> 01:14:04.458
Keep trying his cellphone.

01:14:05.000 --> 01:14:07.791
- I have to announce you.
- How come? Where's Imã?

01:14:07.875 --> 01:14:10.125
Went to a baby clothes manufacturer
with Joca,

01:14:10.208 --> 01:14:13.666
but they are stuck in traffic.
I don't know, some protests.

01:14:17.958 --> 01:14:20.208
"I Don't Believe in Anything Anymore,"

01:14:20.291 --> 01:14:21.250
Paulo Sérgio.

01:14:25.916 --> 01:14:28.083
BODY AND SOUL
FREE

01:14:31.750 --> 01:14:33.625
I don't know what to do

01:14:33.750 --> 01:14:36.625
My life is an endless struggle

01:14:37.250 --> 01:14:39.416
I feel like floating in space

01:14:39.500 --> 01:14:42.250
All the time looking for myself

01:14:43.000 --> 01:14:45.083
There are days in life

01:14:45.166 --> 01:14:47.916
That we think
We're not gonna make it

01:14:48.000 --> 01:14:51.000
That the best thing would be
To run away and escape

01:14:51.083 --> 01:14:54.416
That in another world
Everything will be solved

01:14:54.500 --> 01:14:56.500
I don't know what to do

01:14:56.583 --> 01:14:59.333
If I go back now
Or continue my journey

01:15:00.125 --> 01:15:02.125
I feel so tired

01:15:02.375 --> 01:15:05.375
And I don't know
If it's worth insisting

01:15:05.875 --> 01:15:07.916
There are days in life

01:15:08.458 --> 01:15:10.875
That we think
We're not gonna make it

