I got lost on the road

01:15:22.875 --> 01:15:24.875
I no longer look for love

01:15:25.250 --> 01:15:28.000
I just got used walking alone

01:15:28.083 --> 01:15:30.625
All my life I stepped on thorns

01:15:30.875 --> 01:15:33.500
I realized that my destiny
Is sorrow and pain

01:15:34.041 --> 01:15:35.166
You won't pass!

01:15:41.833 --> 01:15:45.500
It's been so long
since I last joined a protest.

01:15:45.750 --> 01:15:47.375
- By the way--
- Yeah?

01:15:47.583 --> 01:15:50.875
We're so screwed because we got late
thanks to that.

01:15:51.166 --> 01:15:53.500
- Don't worry.
- I don't care, I had fun!

01:15:54.458 --> 01:15:56.583
- Had fun with what?
- What is that?

01:15:59.125 --> 01:16:00.041
Run, Imã! Go!

01:16:00.125 --> 01:16:03.750
Pepe!

01:16:23.125 --> 01:16:26.291
Stop! Not my dad! Get out!

01:16:26.375 --> 01:16:31.666
Stop! Enough! Quit fighting!

01:16:33.125 --> 01:16:34.375
Police!

01:16:34.500 --> 01:16:35.916
Come on, come on!
On the wall!

01:16:36.000 --> 01:16:38.416
On the wall! Get up!
Hands on the head!

01:16:38.500 --> 01:16:40.625
- Busted.
- Hands on the head!

01:16:40.708 --> 01:16:43.125
- Are you okay, dad?
- I'm fine, son.

01:16:43.375 --> 01:16:46.875
- What kind of crap was that?
- Keep an eye on him, Teylor!

01:17:02.750 --> 01:17:03.750
Well...

01:17:04.500 --> 01:17:07.416
The patient had a head injury,

01:17:07.666 --> 01:17:12.041
his left eye sunk in,
multiple fractures of the face bones.

01:17:12.166 --> 01:17:14.583
He is being prepared for surgery.

01:17:14.750 --> 01:17:17.500
Any serious damage to the brain,
doctor?

01:17:17.625 --> 01:17:20.166
Apparently not. I think he will be fine.

01:17:20.250 --> 01:17:22.250
What worries me now

01:17:22.333 --> 01:17:23.666
is his left eye sight.

01:17:36.875 --> 01:17:40.250
I'd like to thank you for what you've done
for all of us.

01:17:41.625 --> 01:17:47.625
Yes, but I'm really sorry
for what happened to Imã and Joca.

01:17:52.000 --> 01:17:54.500
It is not easy to take care
of this family.

01:17:55.750 --> 01:17:57.583
We should hire some backup.

01:17:58.583 --> 01:18:02.791
- I called your cellphone.
- I saw later.

01:18:05.125 --> 01:18:06.916
And then I called your house.

01:18:09.000 --> 01:18:10.541
Your mom is deaf, Odair?

01:18:13.500 --> 01:18:14.333
Yes.

01:18:16.458 --> 01:18:19.750
- But she speaks a little.
- Yes, but it is hard for her.

01:18:21.250 --> 01:18:23.041
It's like walking in the dark.

01:18:26.125 --> 01:18:28.333
She lost her hearing as an adult.

01:18:28.416 --> 01:18:30.666
Degenerative disease.

01:18:33.250 --> 01:18:34.791
Violence victim.

01:18:38.375 --> 01:18:40.166
And why didn't you help her?

01:18:41.958 --> 01:18:44.625
She was expecting me when it all happened.

01:18:44.708 --> 01:18:46.083
And your dad?

01:18:48.083 --> 01:18:49.333
He assaulted her.

01:18:54.375 --> 01:18:55.625
If you excuse me.

01:18:57.000 --> 01:18:57.833
Odair.

01:19:04.958 --> 01:19:06.666
Sometimes I think that...

01:19:08.375 --> 01:19:10.750
it was God who sent you our way.

01:19:14.750 --> 01:19:16.958
I just hope he knows what he's doing.

01:19:48.083 --> 01:19:49.916
Why "volcano," dad?

01:19:50.000 --> 01:19:52.375
I don't know, maybe it has to do
with mythology.

01:19:52.458 --> 01:19:53.708
Mythology?

01:19:53.791 --> 01:19:57.750
Mythology is a bunch of fantastic stories,
with plenty of super heroes.

01:19:57.833 --> 01:20:02.041
Like Wonder Woman,
Spider-Man, Batman.

01:20:03.125 --> 01:20:06.625
When Volcano was born,
his dad tried to kill him.

01:20:08.458 --> 01:20:09.541
But he survived.

01:20:09.625 --> 01:20:11.791
Why did his dad try to kill him?

01:20:16.083 --> 01:20:18.208
So, he could become the god of fire.

01:20:19.083 --> 01:20:22.250
Forge the armor Achilles needed
to win the Trojan war.

01:20:22.791 --> 01:20:24.166
The one with the horse.

01:20:24.708 --> 01:20:25.833
That one.

01:20:26.375 --> 01:20:29.541
A horse created by Odysseus
so they would win the war

01:20:29.625 --> 01:20:31.083
and reunite the family.

01:20:31.166 --> 01:20:33.958
- Did he win?
- He did.

01:20:34.583 --> 01:20:37.750
It took a while, but he did win.

01:20:45.083 --> 01:20:46.750
My flower

01:20:47.416 --> 01:20:49.416
Do not hurt me

01:20:49.541 --> 01:20:51.125
My pain

